      "Required: aria-required='true' en input + indicador visual",
      "Error: aria-invalid='true' + aria-errormessage='[error-id]' apuntando a errorMessage",
      "Helper text: aria-describedby='[helper-id]'",
      "Error message: role='alert' + aria-live='assertive' (inmediato) o 'polite' (summary)",
