  "tokens": { "total": 24, "prefix": "frm", "mode": "C" },
  "componentDescriptions": {
    "FormField": "Campo individual de form: label + input + helper/error/success. State: default/focused/error/success/disabled. Layout: stacked (label arriba) / horizontal (label left) / inline (single line compact). Sizes: sm/md/lg.\n\n🔑 ARIA:\n• <label for='...'> native\n• aria-required + required visual indicator\n• aria-invalid + aria-errormessage en error\n• aria-describedby → helper text\n\n⌨️ Keyboard:\n• Label clickeable mueve focus al input\n\nWCAG 2.2 AA.",
    "FormSection": "Agrupación de FormFields relacionados. Variant: default (spacing visual) / card (borderless container) / inset (con padding + bg).\n\n🔑 ARIA:\n• <fieldset> + <legend> native\n\nWCAG 2.2 AA.",
    "Form": "Layout completo de formulario. Layout: single-column / two-column (form grid) / horizontal (label left alineado). Size: sm/md/lg.\n\n🔑 ARIA:\n• <form> native\n• Submit button explicit\n\n⌨️ Keyboard:\n• Tab order en DOM order\n• Enter submit (si único textfield)\n\n🎯 Focus:\n• Focus al primer field empty al abrir (si form modal)\n• Return focus al trigger al cancelar\n• Error: focus al primer invalid field al submit\n\nTokens: 24, prefijo frm-.\nWCAG 2.2 AA.\n\nForm validation: client-side immediate (on blur) + server-side submit. Error summary opcional en top con links a invalid fields (WCAG 3.3.1)."
  },
  "variableBindings": {
    "frm/field/sm/gap": "spacing/2",
